content: I would like to submit the eLTSS project to be part of the Care Planning track for May. Who is the best person to ask about this?
Who was listed as the track lead last WGM?
I think it was Dave Carlson. (at least he's in the proposal)
There's two Dave Carlsons listed in Zulip. Any idea which one it would be?
@David Pyke I will create the draft proposal page this week for a Care Planning track at the May connectathon. I've worked with Evelyn to coordinate eLTSS use case in previous conntectathons.
